                            <comment id="310854" author="bzzz" created="Mon, 23 Aug 2021 14:15:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not sure - this is an eviction case which means &quot;IO error is possible&quot; ? and this is why we do have clients_up() in fail_abort() ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="310853" author="adilger" created="Mon, 23 Aug 2021 13:57:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Shouldn&apos;t this be handled automatically for the MDS connections, rather than depending on the test framework to fix the connections?  Otherwise there will be issues for systems on real recovery?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
